  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_120",
    "english": "Taimanin. A student of Gosha Academy. A Wind Art user who can manipulate the air using a specially designed umbrella. She uses a ninja art, 'Wind God's Rage', which allows her to create whirlwinds freely. She's also good at protecting allies by using the special alloy umbrella or making storm barriers.\n\nShe hails from a renowned ninja clan and grew up like a princess, so she is shy around strangers.\n\nShe's used to being alone, but feels lonely at the same time. She hopes to get along with many friends in real life, but she has pretty much given up on the idea because of the fear of getting rejected.",
